#### 3. Simplify f-string concatenation in `_decide_research()`
**File**: `backend/research_sweep.py:135-138`
**Type**: Improved clarity
**Before**:
```python
prompt = (
    f"Thing: {thing.title}\n"
    f"Open questions:\n" + "\n".join(f"- {q}" for q in questions)
)
```
**After**:
```python
questions_text = "\n".join(f"- {q}" for q in questions)
prompt = f"Thing: {thing.title}\nOpen questions:\n{questions_text}"
```

---

